### Get Welcome Message
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Create a New Product (Sharee)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Katan Sharee",
    "category": "Sharee",
    "price": 5500,
    "description": "Exclusive SORA Collection Katan Sharee",
    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/katan.jpg",
    "stock": 20
}

### Get All Products
GET http://localhost:5000/api/products